# Personal Portfolio Website

## Overview
This repository contains the source code for my personal portfolio website.  
The site showcases my skills, experiences, and projects in a professional and interactive format.  
It includes a chatbot, QR code integration, GitHub project links, and an updated resume.

## Features
- **Home:** Introduction and welcome section.  
- **About:** Detailed description of skills, experiences, and education.  
- **Projects:** Showcases work with links to GitHub repositories and live demos.  
- **Resume:** Viewable online and downloadable in one click (HTML/PDF).  
- **Contact:** Form for visitors to reach out.  
- **Chatbot:** Simple FAQ chatbot answering questions about skills, tools, projects, and availability.  
- **QR Code:** Direct link to portfolio, displayed on the site and embedded in the resume.  
- **Design:** Dynamic colors, unique dark theme, pixelated horizon scenery background, smooth transitions/animations.  

## Tech Stack
- **Frontend:** HTML, CSS, JavaScript  
- **Chatbot:** Dialogflow or JavaScript-based chatbot library  
- **Version Control:** Git & GitHub  
- **Deployment:** GitHub Pages / Netlify / Vercel  
